{"tid":520023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陸啟用M503航線 美：反對片面行動改變兩岸現狀","createTime":"2018-01-05T03:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T14:49:25.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c7956f6ed4330b7ce256bda453c1f29f46d1f3","tid":520023,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/05/realtime/4396343.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2Frealtime%2F4396343.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=906a8e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對中國大陸民用航空局啟用M503航線北上運行及相關銜接航線，美國國務院表示，美國反對任何一方片面採取行動改變兩岸現狀。<br />\n<br />\n未具名的國務院官員4日透過電子郵件回覆本報記者指出，美方關切北京未經與台灣當局協商，修改在台灣海峽使用的民航航線。<br />\n<br />\n「我們反對任何一方片面採取行動改變兩岸現狀。」國務院官員表示，美方鼓勵北京與台北當局在尊嚴與尊重的基礎上，進行建設性對話；兩岸民航與安全相關問題，應該經由雙方對話決定。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸民用航空局網站4日發布，當天開始啟用M503南向北航線及相關銜接航線，並稱該航線為民航航線，大陸空管部門與台灣方面會保持技術性溝通。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會主委張小月隨後舉行記者會表達嚴正抗議，表示陸方未在兩岸協商溝通的情形下，逕自啟用M503南向北航路及W121、122、123航路，陸方此舉是「刻意以民航包裝對台灣的不當企圖」；我方已要求對岸立即停止相關飛航行動，如陸方一意孤行，將必須承擔任何影響兩岸關係的嚴重後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2912857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F2912857&d=UEqiDeshdO8W%2BcbXLZcSCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d9cf3f60\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2912857</a>"},{"pid":"0f2db3c0aaf42201533e1704dfe436e0e8a7a46b","tid":520023,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"打"},{"pid":"17134aa8727fff0b0a86806ad626bccacc2b23ba","tid":520023,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:00:14.000Z","msg":"美國唔會正式承認台澎主權屬於中國<br />\n因為台澎主權未定<br />\n反對任何改變台海現狀"},{"pid":"be3238bfbb3925e8a9eb3b33a572c025f85f5c53","tid":520023,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27bd7fb319ff2c188142cdc1cb9a468aaa7be956","tid":520023,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be3238bfbb3925e8a9eb3b33a572c025f85f5c53","tid":520023,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/122149_2f4b7204a9dd58da69cb8c512213d21f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F122149_2f4b7204a9dd58da69cb8c512213d21f.png&h=f98b6667&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62cfc85ab41fccf869b2d59473bb0e9e0cf6da4f","tid":520023,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27bd7fb319ff2c188142cdc1cb9a468aaa7be956","tid":520023,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be3238bfbb3925e8a9eb3b33a572c025f85f5c53","tid":520023,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/122149_2f4b7204a9dd58da69cb8c512213d21f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F122149_2f4b7204a9dd58da69cb8c512213d21f.png&h=f98b6667&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0e382a189286469fa3ae28ff3f739d50427d1a","tid":520023,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"支那又陰陰濕濕咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪想用通航做理據證明自己實際控制該區空域，好似釣島巡航常規化咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c14e60009bd9ee3279338e85001a7035210dd8","tid":520023,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"通航之後就有理由派軍機巡航<br />\n台灣到時要日日同支那空軍一齊&quot;護航&quot;<br />\n真係好睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cbb57ebdf85167280e2d9eebca1ece4b0e4e35","tid":520023,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}